name: Weird ReelHorror
description:
Before USING IT PLEASE! read the GUIDE! Version 1.0 is the 1st release, version 0.8 is 2nd release to supplement the 1st release!

do NOT MERGE it without MY permission and share your checkpoint, please!

I spent around 10 to 15 hours for each update and optimize it. I'm not throwing away randomly 10 images and clicking 1 button then release !

If you like what i do, I appreciate it if you support and buy me coffee!

Thank you!

v.1.2.9 has relased.

  • Balanced Weights.

  • Added More Token&Optimized Weights

  • Added 100+ image variations and weights are handled by hand.(me!).

  • Added "many limbs" class to make addition limbs.

  • Added "many eyes" class to make addition ( blackend eyes) ( not perfect but it is okay)

  • Added "centipede" class to make realistic infused centipedes into scene. ( succeded. )

  • Added "stomach_mouth" class to get mouth on belly but it is still wip.

  • Added " mouth face" class to get a whole mouth as a face. ( wip )

Useful tags;

  • Centipede

  • many limps

  • many eyes

  • humanoid

  • indoors

  • outdoors

  • blood

  • dismembered

  • dismembered body,

  • pov

  • trash

  • messy

    v1.2

  • v1.2 has relased.

  • 0.8 alternate and v1.0 has merged.

  • some writings are cropped, so probability of getting writings are reduced from outputs. But there is still chance that you get some.

  • Because of more than 100+ additional high resolution sources and balanced weights, you will get better results than vanilla version.

This is my 2nd model. I've been working on 4 days beacause i had over 100+ images and autocaptioning was not fit for this style. That's why i called it weird reelhorror.

====

To use it properly, add lora tag and "reelhorror" keyword.

But if you want to have interesting results, i have a list for you to use and i strongly recommend it to use.

keywords list:

1- 1girl

2- 1boy

3- humanoid

4- tentacles

-- 4.1 - multiple arms

5-blood

--5.1 - dismembered

6- drooling

7- trash

8- indoor

9- outdoors

10- pov

====

Since it is not a usual style, it was hard to describe it into keyword pile. I'm not totaly satisfied the result yet, it is looking better than i've imagined.

  • Alt edition v0.8

This is not a downgrade! It is a supplementary update to help better recognition for few " concepts".

I didn't merge them with training it is because i had to handle extra 150+ images and their captioning by hand. But i found out as a supplementary addition, it gives more details while working together if you add them seperately.

If you want to make thing works when you use both of them, make sure when you add "reelalthorror" tag, use those concepts to get better results,

  • eyes

  • extra eyes

  • blood

  • tentacles

  • horn

  • flesh

  • veins

  • multiple legs ( this might not work, sometimes it is hard to get )

  • ribs

  • teeth

  • open mouth

  • mouth

  • multiple eyes

Those keywords, will give you better results after the supplementary lora tag and trigger word.
